            bindings = <
         &kp Q             &kp W        &kp E       &kp R        &kp T        &kp Y    &kp U       &kp I       &kp O        &kp P
         &mt LEFT_SHIFT A  &mt LCTRL S  &mt LGUI D  &mt LALT F   &kp G        &kp H    &mt RALT J  &mt LGUI K  &mt LCTRL L  &mt LEFT_SHIFT SEMICOLON
&kp TAB  &kp Z             &kp X        &kp C       &kp V        &kp B        &kp N    &kp M       &kp COMMA   &kp DOT      &kp FSLH                  &mt DOUBLE_QUOTES SQT
