            bindings = <
        &trans  &trans  &trans  &trans  &trans    &trans  &kp HOME      &kp UP_ARROW  &kp END        &kp PG_UP
        &trans  &trans  &trans  &trans  &trans    &trans  &kp LEFT      &kp DOWN      &kp RIGHT      &trans
&trans  &trans  &trans  &trans  &trans  &trans    &trans  &kp LA(LEFT)  &trans        &kp LA(RIGHT)  &kp PG_DN  &kp CAPS
                        &trans  &trans  &trans    &trans  &trans        &trans
